<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SPORTMATCH — 서버 오류</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>
<div class="error-page">
  <div class="error-bg-number">500</div>

  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center">
    <div class="error-emoji">💥</div>
    <div class="error-code">500 · Internal Server Error</div>
    <div class="error-title">서버에서 문제가 생겼어요</div>
    <div class="status-row">
      <div class="status-pill"><div class="status-dot"></div> DB 정상</div>
      <div class="status-pill"><div class="status-dot red"></div> API 오류</div>
      <div class="status-pill"><div class="status-dot"></div> 인증 정상</div>
    </div>
    <div class="error-desc">
      저희 서버에서 예상치 못한 오류가 발생했어요.<br>
      팀이 빠르게 확인 중이에요. 잠시 후 다시 시도해 주세요.
    </div>
    <div class="error-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="location.reload()">🔄 새로고침</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="location.href='/'">🏠 홈으로</button>
    </div>

    <% if (typeof stack !== 'undefined' && stack) { %>
    <div class="stack-box">
      <div class="stack-header">
        <div class="stack-label">Error Stack</div>
        <div class="stack-dots">
          <div class="stack-dot" style="background:#FF5F57"></div>
          <div class="stack-dot" style="background:#FEBC2E"></div>
          <div class="stack-dot" style="background:#28C840"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-pre"><%= stack %></div>
    </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
